strip=all&#038;crop=0,0,100,100\" />\n\t<figcaption></figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">The <strong>best AMES 85 loadout </strong>in<em> <em><em><a href=\"https://www.polygon.com/game/call-of-duty-black-ops-6/443261\">Black Ops 6</a></em></em> </em>firmly cements this fully automatic assault rifle near the top of the pecking order as one of the best in the game. Much like the <a href=\"https://www.polygon.com/black-ops-6-guides/470831/best-xm4-loadout-class-build-setup-bo6\">XM4</a>, this is a solid all-rounder that excels at mid-long range with the right attachments.</p>\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">Sitting near the top of our list of the <a href=\"https://www.polygon.com/black-ops-6-guides/470851/best-guns-weapons-meta-bo6\">best gun", "id": 1402366, "language": null, "link": "https://www.polygon.com/black-ops-6-guides/471078/best-ames-85-loadout-class-build-setup-bo6", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 85, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 258, "source_url": "https://www.polygon.com/rss/index.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": null, "title": "Best AMES 85 loadout and class build setup in Black Ops 6", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-10-28T11:30:00+00:00", "description": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<figure>\n\n<img alt=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-portal-copyright=\"\" data-has-syndication-rights=\"1\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/10/BbPpBbcdRrr8839bB_1600x1080.png?quality=90&#038;strip=all&#038;crop=0,0,100,100\" />\n\t<figcaption></figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\"><em>Foundations</em>, the next expansion for Magic: The Gathering, arrives Nov. 15 and aims at providing a fun, accessible experience for every level of play. The expansion draws from a variety of aesthetics and reintroduces some of the game\u2019s most famous cards, which will be legal in all standard formats through 2029.</p>\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">While <em>Foundations</em> will launch with a pair of new products intended to onboard new players, veterans looking to expand their collection may find some great additions in the typical spread of Booster Boxes and Bundles. We\u2019ve outlined all of the products available in this expansion below and where", "id": 1401928, "language": null, "link": "https://www.polygon.com/pre-order/468130/magic-the-gathering-mtg-foundations-where-to-buy", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 85, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 258, "source_url": "https://www.polygon.com/rss/index.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": null, "title": "Where to pre-order Magic: The Gathering &#8211; Foundations", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-10-28T10:17:34+00:00", "description": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<figure>\n\n<img alt=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-portal-copyright=\"\" data-has-syndication-rights=\"1\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/10/171354_2462_R.jpg?quality=90&#038;strip=all&#038;crop=0,0,100,72.08203125\" />\n\t<figcaption></figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">When David Henrie and Selena Gomez sat down to develop a sequel for <a href=\"https://www.polygon.com/disney-plus/2019/11/18/20962882/disney-plus-channel-original-movie-list-best-of-dcom-top-10-high-school-movie\">Disney Channel</a> fantasy sitcom&nbsp;<em>Wizards of Waverly Place</em>, they knew they had a challenge ahead of them. Henrie and Gomez played overachiever Justin and snarky slacker Alex, respectively, during the show\u2019s original run, when the characters were teenagers. This time around, though, the actors are also behind the camera as executive producers.&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">\u201cWe wanted the same spirit, the same heart, the same h", "id": 1401344, "language": null, "link": "https://www.polygon.com/preview/470633/wizards-beyond-waverly-place-sequel-david-henrie", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating": 27, "page_rating_contents": 85, "page_rating_visits": 0, "page_rating_votes": 0, "permanent": false, "source__id": 258, "source_url": "https://www.polygon.com/rss/index.xml", "status_code": 0, "tags": [], "thumbnail": null, "title": "David Henrie reveals what makes the Wizards of Waverly Place sequel work", "vote": 0}, {"age": null, "album": "", "artist": null, "bookmarked": false, "comments": [], "date_published": "2024-10-28T10:07:28+00:00", "description": "\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n<figure>\n\n<img alt=\"\" data-caption=\"\" data-portal-copyright=\"\" data-has-syndication-rights=\"1\" src=\"https://platform.polygon.com/wp-content/uploads/sites/2/2024/10/AnimalCrossingPocketCampComplete_1x1_KeyArt.jpg?quality=90&#038;strip=all&#038;crop=0,0,100,100\" />\n\t<figcaption></figcaption>\n</figure>\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">Nintendo\u2019s free-to-play mobile version of <a href=\"https://www.polygon.com/nintendo/442905/animal-crossing-pocket-camp-shut-down\">Animal Crossing is closing down on Nov. 28</a>. Just a few days later, that game will be reborn in a paid, offline version called <em>Animal Crossing: Pocket Camp Complete</em>, which will cost $9.99 at launch on Dec. 2, <a href=\"https://ac-pocketcamp.com/en-US/topics/ANNOUNCEMENT_2410242\">Nintendo announced Sunday</a>.</p>\n\n<p class=\"has-text-align-none\">That introductory price will run through Jan. 31, 2025. After that, <em>Animal Crossing: Pocket Camp Complete</em> will cost $19.99.</p>\n\n<p class=\"has-text-", "id": 1401345, "language": null, "link": "https://www.polygon.com/news/470977/animal-crossing-pocket-camp-complete-paid-version", "manual_status_code": 0, "page_rating":